    "name": "Horizon Journey",
    "steam_appid": 1769960,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/c5b21769ca7ca109e40946beb00c9da3.poster.avif?t=1769760058\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/c5b21769ca7ca109e40946beb00c9da3.webm?t=1769760058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/c5b21769ca7ca109e40946beb00c9da3.mp4?t=1769760058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《地平线之旅》中开启一场前往火星的史诗冒险，这是一款开放世界生存游戏，将殖民、地球化和探索相结合，支持单人游戏和多人合作模式。故事设定在2053年，你是第17次奋进任务的一员，承担着将火星变成人类新家园的艰巨任务。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真实的火星景观：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验前所未有的火星环境，基于真实的NASA图像。探索令人惊叹、严酷而神秘的红色星球景观，拥有精准的环境设置和光照效果。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/35b2c9ea19271f4afd4dd17a4103eceb.poster.avif?t=1769760058\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/35b2c9ea19271f4afd4dd17a4103eceb.webm?t=1769760058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/35b2c9ea19271f4afd4dd17a4103eceb.mp4?t=1769760058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存与殖民：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在收集资源、建造结构和地球化火星表面的过程中平衡生存与殖民的努力。使用模块化建筑系统定制你的基地，确保每个部分都能独特地满足你的需求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单人和多人合作：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以单人游戏或与朋友合作探索。共同探索遥远的地区，收集资源，并防御火星潜在的危险。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/2aabebc175997b105dd70f61556c3f40.poster.avif?t=1769760058\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/2aabebc175997b105dd70f61556c3f40.webm?t=1769760058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/2aabebc175997b105dd70f61556c3f40.mp4?t=1769760058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索和资源收集：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入探究过去任务的残骸，在旧殖民区搜寻珍贵矿物和隐藏的宝藏。使用配备热成像、夜视和矿业挖掘扫描仪的高级漫游车，发现偏远地区和地下资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意火星表面下隐藏的危险。旧殖民区可能隐藏着超出肉眼可见的东西。为每种情况做好准备。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/7a064de35024e74b70eeb46ce9715bcf.poster.avif?t=1769760058\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/7a064de35024e74b70eeb46ce9715bcf.webm?t=1769760058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/7a064de35024e74b70eeb46ce9715bcf.mp4?t=1769760058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>先进的技术和车辆：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用专为远程探索设计的车辆，配备扩展的储物舱和生存储备。发现未知的技术组件，提升你的工具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>综合制作系统：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握复杂的制作系统，通过矿藏开采，使用各种开发中的分支组件，并组合子组件以生产最终产品。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/d6ade4587e7938568f816f2492f284bb.poster.avif?t=1769760058\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/d6ade4587e7938568f816f2492f284bb.webm?t=1769760058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/d6ade4587e7938568f816f2492f284bb.mp4?t=1769760058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态大气条件：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在火星极端环境下生存，包括沙尘暴、辐射区和温度波动。管理你的健康、氧气、饥饿和口渴，同时应对可能损坏设备和威胁生存的环境挑战。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>资源管理：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集金融资产和珍贵矿物，调整资源比例，使用专业工具管理殖民地的需求。利用独特的生产改进装置，包括人工食品合成器、材料转换合成器、水族箱单元和分析台，所有这些都连接到殖民地的电力系统。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/d238d6ed17e2a89e9258a38f0f02122a.poster.avif?t=1769760058\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/d238d6ed17e2a89e9258a38f0f02122a.webm?t=1769760058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769960/extras/d238d6ed17e2a89e9258a38f0f02122a.mp4?t=1769760058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加入冒险之旅！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《地平线之旅》中，每一个决定都至关重要。探索广袤的火星景观，揭开过去任务的秘密，建立繁荣的殖民地，你将塑造人类在火星上的未来。你准备好迎接终极生存挑战，在红色星球上留下你的印记吗？</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 简体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 土耳其语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
